org.nlpcraft.model.tools.dump

Class NCDumpReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nlpcraft.model.tools.dump.NCDumpReader

  • public class NCDumpReader
extends Object
    Data model dump reader.

    Data model dump allows to export the model and intent configuration sans the callback implementations. Data model dumps can be used to safely test model's intent-based matching logic by a 3rd party.
    See Also:
    NCDumpWriter, NCModelBuilder.loadFromDump(String)

    • Method Detail

      • read

        public static NCModel read(String filePath)
                    throws NCException
        Reads the data model dump and creates data model proxy.
        Parameters:
        filePath - Data model dump file path to read.
        Returns:
        Data model proxy. Proxy will have a no-op callback implementations for intent and will return the following JSON response: 
         {
     "modelId": "model-id",
     "intentId": "intent-id",
     "modelFile": "model-id-01:01:01:123.gz"
  }
        Throws:
        NCException - Thrown in case of any errors.
        See Also:
        NCModelBuilder.loadFromDump(String)
